{"tid":720900,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[企開d啦]【世界盃E、F組】大誇金英權射垮德國　內媒：這夜屬於中超","createTime":"2018-06-28T09:35:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-28T11:39:33.000Z","uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"2afba914cb8d9ec79205e03bed809d1ae8749c8f","tid":720900,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T09:35:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180628/s00006/1530175945829\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180628%2Fs00006%2F1530175945829&d=FnQ%2F9mtAayapiHTGFvsBm0kviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=c9b128f5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180628%2Fs00006%2F1530175945829&h=3071e050\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180628/s00006/1530175945829</a><br />\n<br />\n韓國後衛金英權在世界盃F組壓軸一戰，尾段入球擊敗衛冕之師德國，令對手包尾出局。內地多間傳媒報道賽果時均特別註明，金英權是現役中超球員，這次是首度有中超球員在世界盃進球。一些報道中也提到，數小時後E組賽事中，前廣州恒大球員荷西保連奴為巴西建功，總結兩場比賽曰：「這一夜的世界盃，除了屬於巴西和韓國，亦是屬於中超的。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n韓國28歲後衛金英權是今屆9名中超球員其中一員，內地傳媒大讚金英權「射垮德國」、「用表現證明中超沒有令他退步」。他在90分鐘入球，令韓國領先，之後再有孫興慜建功助韓國以2：0擊敗德國。雖然最終出局，韓國在得分榜上反壓對手升上小組第3，德國則跌到末位，黯然在世界盃分組賽出局。<br />\n<br />\n去年由廣州恒大加盟巴塞隆拿的巴西中場荷西保連奴，之後在E組面對哥斯達黎加亦有進帳，最終森巴軍團贏2：0排小組首名出線。有內地傳媒報道時，標題寫明〈最大贏家是廣州恒大〉，認為「這一夜的世界盃同時也屬於中國的」。<br />\n<br />\n翻查資料，金英權在所屬中超球會上陣機會近來愈來愈少，有傳他更將於今季離隊。他在對陣德國賽後回應：「我這4年過得很辛苦，這次勝利讓我們獲得一點安慰，我將繼續貢獻韓國足球。"},{"pid":"27b93425d67af094477a29a9998d1cc7b6a5b008","tid":720900,"uid":143940,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T09:37:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁都可以打飛機"},{"pid":"d4a7691d4cddea8207326c2f201674e7da5606ed","tid":720900,"uid":8171,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T09:44:36.000Z","msg":"中國又成最大贏家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9910358b651955667b46e6e9f47dc8b6ffff6bdf","tid":720900,"uid":44358,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T09:44:46.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">中蟈</span></span></strong>又成為最後贏家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1c53a6654004304e584cee8edf1866f13e83e53","tid":720900,"uid":31675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T10:10:49.000Z","msg":"贏國<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3433e563360a2397d142ace06c11eac640c6c33","tid":720900,"uid":41205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T10:11:54.000Z","msg":"想睇班支那球迷咩反應<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b78bea4fc107fd5816ba942c35b31f76b0b80b74","tid":720900,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T10:17:50.000Z","msg":"&hellip;無言"},{"pid":"f4f26d68561de069e87dffd2db42cb16d34eb203","tid":720900,"uid":58552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T10:18:31.000Z","msg":"我真撚係寫個服字畀贏國<br />\n我真係服"},{"pid":"446d39951a9b54b6c6e82e7de9ab1693182f19dc","tid":720900,"uid":112935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T10:20:09.000Z","msg":"又起度認屎認屁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9de03c91f5df530f1e9aff3ffbf8468cdc9904e9","tid":720900,"uid":184966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T10:23:06.000Z","msg":"只能說明南韓球員百毒不侵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccbd2d6633ba726e6c2